<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>500 - Server Error | Zyrox</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" />
    <!-- Google Fonts - Inter -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-deep: #0a0c14;
            --bg-card: #111422;
            --error-red: #ef4444;
            --error-glow: rgba(239, 68, 68, .2);
            --text-1: #f0f2ff;
            --text-2: #8b92b8;
            --transition: .22s cubic-bezier(.4, 0, .2, 1);
        }

        body {
            background: var(--bg-deep);
            color: var(--text-1);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 75% -10%, rgba(239, 68, 68, .08) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 30% at 10% 90%, rgba(79, 110, 247, .05) 0%, transparent 60%);
        }

        .error-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 10;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            animation: fadeIn .8s ease;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 10rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            line-height: .8;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text-1) 0%, #4f566b 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            opacity: .1;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            user-select: none;
        }

        .icon-circle {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: var(--bg-card);
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, .2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: var(--error-red);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, .4), 0 0 20px var(--error-glow);
            position: relative;
        }

        .icon-circle::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(239, 68, 68, .1);
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: scale(1.3); opacity: 0; }
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }

        .error-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-2);
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .btn-action {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: .8rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--error-red) 0%, #ff6b6b 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1.1rem 2.8rem;
            border-radius: 99px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(239, 68, 68, .3);
            transition: all var(--transition);
        }

        .btn-action:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(239, 68, 68, .4);
            color: #fff;
        }

        .floating-elements {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .element {
            position: absolute;
            background: var(--error-red);
            opacity: .03;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="error-code">500</div>

    <div class="error-wrapper">
        <div class="icon-circle">
            <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill"></i>
        </div>

        <h1 class="error-title">System <span>Glitch</span></h1>
        <p class="error-subtitle">
            Something went wrong on our end. We're already working to fix it. <br class="d-none d-md-block">
            Please try again in a few moments.
        </p>

        <a href="/" class="btn-action">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i>
            Back to Safety
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="floating-elements">
        <div class="element" style="width: 300px; height: 300px; top: -150px; right: -150px;"></div>
        <div class="element" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; bottom: 10%; left: -50px;"></div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
